from hashlib import sha256
HASH = 'c22a563acc2a587afbfaaaa6d67bc6e628872b00bd7e998873881f7c6fdc62fc'
phone_base = '861709'
for i in range(10 ** 8):
    phone = phone_base + str(i).zfill(8)
    if sha256(phone.encode()).hexdigest() == HASH:
        print(phone)
